  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "First, listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Why did Patrick keep on asking the same question?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "帕特里克为什么一再问同一个问题？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "The former Prime Minister, Mr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "前首相温特沃思·莱恩先生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Wentworth Lane, was defeated in the recent elections.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "在最近的选举中落败了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Patrick has always been a fanatical opponent of Mr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "帕特里克一向是莱恩先生所领导的"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "Lane's radical progressive party.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "激进进步党的狂热反对者。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "After the elections, Patrick went to the former Prime Minister's house.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "选举结束后，帕特里克来到前首相的住所。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "When he asked if Mr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他询问莱恩先生是否住在那里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Lane lived there, the policeman on duty told him that since his defeat, the ex-Prime Minister had gone abroad.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "值勤警察告诉他，自从落选后，这位前首相已经出国了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "On the following day, Patrick went to the house again.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第二天，帕特里克又来到那所房子。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "The same policeman was just walking slowly past the entrance when Patrick asked the same question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "同一名警察正在门口缓缓巡逻，帕特里克又问了同样的问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "Though a little suspicious this time, the policeman gave him the same answer.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "警察这次虽然有些疑心，还是给了他同样的回答。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "The day after, Patrick went to the house once more and asked exactly the same question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "又过了一天，帕特里克再次来到那所房子，问了完全相同的问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "This time, the policeman lost his temper.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这一次，警察发火了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "I told you yesterday and the day before yesterday, he shouted.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我昨天和前天都告诉过你了，”他喊道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "Mr.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "莱恩先生。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "Lane was defeated in the elections.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“莱恩先生在选举中落败了。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "He has retired from political life and gone to live abroad.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“他已经退出政坛，搬到国外生活去了。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "I know, answered Patrick, but I love to hear you say it.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我知道，”帕特里克回答，“但我就是喜欢听你这么说。”"
      }
    }
  ],
